| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-0261 — Recovery Inhibition (fulcrumsec)"
| comment "Status: stable | Level: high | ID: cbf9d2e7-95af-5ffb-b3e7-d5a02f824511"
